    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl py-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">Got New Project?</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 mb-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">With our expert guidance, we facilitate the growth of your business.</p>
